!! Restart rules

|!Change |!Restart needed? |
|`orchestrator.js`, `adapter-*.js`, `tool-executor.js`, `context-resolver.js`, `file-resolver.js` |Yes ‚Äî `module-type: library`, loaded at boot |
|`chat-widget.js`, `action-widget.js` |Yes ‚Äî `module-type: widget`, loaded at boot |
|`startup.js`, `ui/drag-panel.js` |Yes ‚Äî `module-type: startup`, loaded at boot |
|Tool tiddlers (tagged `$:/tags/rimir/llm-connect/tool`) |No ‚Äî read from wiki store per invocation |
|Context templates, prompt templates |No ‚Äî read from wiki store per request |
|Config tiddlers (`$:/config/rimir/llm-connect/*`) |No ‚Äî read from wiki store per request |
|UI tiddlers (`ui/chat-panel.tid`, `ui/pair-edit*.tid`) |Browser reload ‚Äî system tiddlers |

<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/doc-template/templates/callout" type="tip">
<$fill $name="body">
On Windows, use `taskkill //F //PID <pid> //T` to kill the server before restarting.
</$fill>
</$transclude>

!! Key modules

|!Module |!Type |!Role |
|`orchestrator.js` |library |Tool-use loop, conversation management, HTTP requests, `file_ref` resolution |
|`adapter-claude.js` |library |Claude API: request building, response parsing, multimodal blocks |
|`adapter-openai.js` |library |OpenAI API: same interface, different format |
|`adapter-azure.js` |library |Azure OpenAI API: deployment/version config |
|`tool-executor.js` |library |Tool dispatch, restricted wiki proxy, wikitext execution |
|`context-resolver.js` |library |Template precedence, rendering, context attachment resolution |
|`file-resolver.js` |library |File detection, classification (image/document), base64 fetching |
|`chat-widget.js` |widget |`<$llm-chat>` ‚Äî chat UI, message management, debug panel |
|`action-widget.js` |widget |`<$llm-action>` ‚Äî one-shot invocation, output writing |

!! Debugging

* Use the debug panel (bug icon) in the chat to inspect the request payload before sending
* Check `$:/temp/rimir/llm-connect/write-log` for the audit log of all write operations
* Tool tiddlers can be cloned and edited from Settings > Tools ‚Äî clones start disabled
* Set `tool-enabled: no` on work-in-progress tools to prevent them from being used

!! Dependencies

* ''theme'' ‚Äî CSS utility classes (`rr-*` prefix)

</$fill>
</$transclude>
